text: Aygulevo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Aygulevsky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 641 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Sterlitamak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Aygulevo
